raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
do social_post(\"naomi_earlybird\")
Player: Morning!
Player: What are you up to?
Mabel: 🤫
Mabel: I'm in class babe
Mabel: I can't text!
Player: You're literally texting me right now 😀
Mabel: What? 
Mabel: No I'm not!
Mabel: Wait
Mabel: I am, omg
Mabel: 😵‍💫
Mabel: Gotta go!
Mabel: But I wanna show you something later 🫢
Player: 😆
=> END"
